des:
SmartVU Home products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your lights.
There's no need to go to the switch to adjust your lights - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your SmartVU Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "SmartVU Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "SmartVU Home" app;
(3). You need to have some SmartVU Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "SmartVU Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "SmartVU Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "SmartVU Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "SmartVU Home", and you'll be navigated to "SmartVU Home" login page;
(9). Input your SmartVU Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light."
"Alexa, turn off the bedroom light."
"Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%."
"Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%."
"Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
